---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const APP_URL = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_APP_URL ?? 'https://app.myground.work';
---
<Layout title="How it works · Groundwork" description="Define the situation. Everyone checks in privately. Groundwork shows where accounts agree and where they differ. No meetings, no bias, no guesswork." canonicalPath="/how-it-works">
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{margin:0;overflow-x:hidden}
    .gw-nav-link{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:#6B6560;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:6px 11px;border-radius:6px;font-family:inherit;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;}
    .gw-nav-link:hover{background:#E8E6E3;color:#1A1916;}
    .gw-btn-ghost{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#0C447C;background:none;border:1px solid #B5D4F4;cursor:pointer;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:6px;font-family:inherit;white-space:nowrap;transition:background .15s;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;}
    .gw-btn-ghost:hover{background:#EEF4FB;}
    .gw-btn-solid{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;background:#0C447C;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:6px;font-family:inherit;white-space:nowrap;transition:background .15s;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;}
    .gw-btn-solid:hover{background:#1557A0;}
    .gw-footer-btn{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
    .gw-footer-btn:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);}
    @media(max-width:620px){
      .gw-nav-links{display:none !important;}
    }
  </style>

  <div style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;background:#EDECEA;min-height:100vh;color:#1A1916;">

    <nav style="position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(237,236,234,.96);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border-bottom:1px solid #E2E0DB;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 20px;height:56px;">
      <a href="/" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;text-decoration:none;">
        <svg width="20" height="16" viewBox="0 0 22 17" fill="none">
          <rect x="5"  y="0"  width="12" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#0C447C" opacity="0.45"/>
          <rect x="2"  y="6"  width="18" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#0C447C" opacity="0.72"/>
          <rect x="0"  y="12" width="22" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#0C447C"/>
        </svg>
        <span style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0C447C;letter-spacing:-.02em;">Groundwork</span>
      </a>
      <div class="gw-nav-links" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2px;">
        <a class="gw-nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="gw-nav-link" href="/how-it-works" style="background:#E8E6E3;color:#1A1916;">How it works</a>
        <a class="gw-nav-link" href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a class="gw-nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-shrink:0;">
        <a class="gw-btn-ghost" href={`${APP_URL}/auth`}>Sign in</a>
        <a class="gw-btn-solid" href={`${APP_URL}/start`}>Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:56px 24px 80px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0C447C;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px;">How it works</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1916;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:16px;">Two sides. One clear picture.</h1>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:48px;">You say what you need. Your team says what they understood. You see the gap.</p>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;margin-bottom:48px;">
        <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E0DB;">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#0C447C;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;">1</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px;">Write down what you need done</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.7;">What did you tell them? What does success look like? What was agreed and by when? The clearer you are here, the more useful everything that follows will be.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E0DB;">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#0C447C;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;">2</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px;">Your team answers privately in their own words</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.7;">Each person says what they understood, what they have done, what is blocking them, and what support they need. Nobody can see each other's answers before the report is ready. That is the point. It is the only way to get what people actually think rather than what they think you want to hear.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E0DB;">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#0C447C;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;">3</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px;">You see what landed and what did not</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.7;">Where people are in sync you will see it. Where there is a gap you will see exactly who thought what, how far apart things are, and what the gap is costing you.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;padding:24px 0;">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:#085041;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;">4</div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px;">You know exactly what to fix</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.7;">Not a vague note to improve communication. Specific people, specific misunderstandings, specific next steps. The report tells you what to address and who to speak to.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#F5F3EF;border-radius:10px;padding:24px;border:1px solid #E2E0DB;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <h3 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:8px;">What you actually create</h3>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;">Every Ground has a situation, a set of participants, a check-in frequency, and a set of questions. Here is what one looks like.</p>
        <div style="background:white;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #E2E0DB;padding:16px 20px;font-size:13px;color:#1A1916;line-height:2.2;">
          <div><strong>What we are working on:</strong> Launch MarketView in Lagos by September</div>
          <div><strong>Participants:</strong> 12 team members</div>
          <div><strong>Check-in frequency:</strong> Weekly</div>
          <div><strong>Questions:</strong> What did you complete? What is blocking you? What do you need?</div>
          <div><strong>Progress:</strong> Week 1 complete. Week 2 complete. Week 3 in progress.</div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#9B9590;margin-top:12px;margin-bottom:0;">You create one of these for any situation where more than one person needs to be working toward the same thing.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <a class="gw-btn-solid" href={`${APP_URL}/start`} style="padding:13px 28px;font-size:14px;">Start your first Ground free</a>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer style="background:#0A1628;padding:32px 24px;text-align:center;">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:9px;margin-bottom:16px;">
        <svg width="18" height="14" viewBox="0 0 22 17" fill="none">
          <rect x="5"  y="0"  width="12" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="white" opacity="0.45"/>
          <rect x="2"  y="6"  width="18" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="white" opacity="0.72"/>
          <rect x="0"  y="12" width="22" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="white"/>
        </svg>
        <span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);">Groundwork</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:20px;">
        <a class="gw-footer-btn" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="gw-footer-btn" href="/how-it-works">How it works</a>
        <a class="gw-footer-btn" href="/use-cases">Use cases</a>
        <a class="gw-footer-btn" href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a class="gw-footer-btn" href="/about">About</a>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);margin:0;">&#169; 2025 Groundwork.</p>
    </footer>

  </div>
</Layout>
